data.description: **MOTIVATED SELLER! Another price reduction and a $10k seller-paid credit towards closing costs or rate buy-down. Book a showing now!**  Investors and weekend warriors, welcome to a gem in the rough, on an oversized lot!  This large home has many modern amenities such as an updated electric panel, heat pump, pellet stove, newer appliances, plenty of storage space, and skylights providing plenty of natural light. The primary bedroom with an ensuite bath has French doors that lead to the private back patio.  Must see to appreciate the potential of this property!  This, coupled with a delightful fully fenced backyard, with raised beds fruit trees and an outdoor shed will make a great home for families and gardening enthusiasts.  The entire home also has a maintenance-free metal roof.Shopping is nearby and close to the 5 Fwy providing added convenience.The home is being sold AS-IS.  Seller to do no repairs.Staying: W/D stackable, oven(brand new), dishwasher(brand new), refrigerator, and upright freezer.Not Staying:  Aluminum Rampo (backyard), boxes of flooring, and camera systemOPEN HOUSE:  Saturday and Sunday (9/16-17) from 12:00 to 2:00 p.m.The offer deadline will be set upon the first acceptable offer received.
